Sun Co's Sun Refining and Marketingsubsidiary said it increased the price it charges contractbarge customers for heating oil in New York harbor 0.50 cent agallon, effective today.    They said the 0.50 cent increase brings Sun's contractbarge price to 49 cts. The recent price hike represents thefifth this week, totalling 4.75 cts. The increases arefollowing sharp spot and futures price rises, the company said. Reuter&#3;